      "text": "Peeminni mannis/mans\nDeews! eekch ta/ un ne isdełdi\nmannu Labdarrischanu/ ko es pee\nta Namma manna Deewa / un\npee winna Sargaschanahm dar-\nrijs efimu."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
