      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi juhsu Tehwi ta\ndarrija/ un muhtu Deews wedde\nwiﬀu scho Nelaimi pahr mums/\nun pahr scho Pilstahtu? Un juhs\npeeleekat pee tahs karstas Bahr-\ndsibas pahr Israëlu wehl wairak/\npahrkahpdamt to fwehtu Deenu."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas notikkahs pretti\nSwehdeenas Laika / kad ta\n(Saule) no Jerusalemes Wahrt-\ntim bija atstahjusi/ tad pawehle-\nju es/ ka tahm Durwim bij ais-\nflehgtahn tapt/ ka tahs ne bija\natdarriht/ famehr ta Swehdee-\nna pagahjust. Un es liku no\nmanneem Puifscheem pee tahm\nWahrtim/ ka nekahda Nasta tur\neenahktu Swehdeenâ."
    },
