      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad palikfe tee Sahtu-\nPrezzineeki/ un wiﬀadas Prez-\nzes Pahrdeweji zaar Nakti abra\npreeksch Jerusalemes/ tahdas Di-\nwi Reisas."
